channel.title: How could I edit a 508 server?
channel.description:
I downloaded a 508 server and it's much different then the normal one's :s... i can't find any Client.java
, and also, there is no Compile button.
Please help me :|
Greetz, tha hartpaint TEAM

item.title: How could I edit a 508 server?
item.dc:creator: @tonypker13 tonypker13
item.description:
@tonypker13 wrote:

Compiler? {CMD folder, Titled ‘All’}
Client.java? {No need. All Java files you would need are in the SRC folder.}
